Argentum Studio – a company that creates high quality cinematics in Unreal Engine and other software

At Argentum Studio, we turn your creative ideas into reality by offering top-notch CGI solutions. We are a team of talented CG artists specializing in providing high-quality 3D art services for cinematics, trailers, music videos and creative advertising projects worldwide. Using the latest Unreal Engine 5 rendering engine, we achieve superior quality and fast results.

Our passionate and highly skilled artists create impressive CG characters, environments, animations, groom and other assets. We combine a creative approach with precise technical execution. From character development to environment creation, we meet the diverse needs of 3D art.

Our services:
• Character/creature modeling and design;
• Environment modeling and design/Lighting;
• Grooming (hair/fur modelling);
• Character FX;
• Real-time VFX creation and rendering;
• Creative creations;
• Character animation and rigging;
• 2D Concept/Animation;
• Full or partial cycle cinematic creation in Unreal Engine 5.

High Quality: We are proud to produce top-level 3D art, which needs minimum revisions by clients. Every project is made to meet your unique requirements and bring your creative vision to life.

Partnership Approach: We believe in the power of collaboration. We stick to your ideas and enhance them through our artistic expertise.

Deadline Adherence: We understand the importance of timelines. We apply efficient workflow controls, so that your project can always be released on time.

Flexibility and Versatility: Our team can adapt to any aesthetic of your project, whether it’s realistic renders, stylized concepts, or something in between. We are happy to bring any of your ideas to life.

