Abu Dhabi Film Commission was launched in 2009 to support the development of Abu Dhabi’s film and TV industry, and promote the Emirate of Abu Dhabi as a production location, regionally and internationally.

We are passionate about the film and TV business.  At the core of our DNA is a love of TV and film. We understand what is needed to create quality content, and what those who make it expect of us.

Our responsibility is to assist production companies through every step of the production process, including:
- Accessing the generous 30% cash rebate on production spend
- Free scouting assistance and finding a diverse range of unique locations;
- Assisting with the procedures to obtain shooting permits, visas, script approval, and customs clearance;
- Finding award-winning, experienced professional crew and supplier bases;
- Finding first class studios and post-production facilities at competitive rates
- Advice on superb accommodations and restaurants that will make you feel at home
- Well, we shouldn’t take the credit for it but we also offer year-round sunshine and blue sky

Established in 1984, WBImages is the official international promotion agency for the audio-visual arts and industry of the Walloon-Brussels Community.

WBImages is co-financed and co-managed by the Centre du Cinéma et de l’Audiovisuel and Wallonie Bruxelles International.

Its mission is :

– to promote audio-visual works from Wallonia-Brussels at international festival and market events;
– to facilitate Walloon-Brussels audio-visual professionals’ access to the audio-visual market and to help them promote and sell their productions at international market events;
- act as the information desk for producers and export agents working in Wallonia-Brussels as well as for buyers, distributors and international audio-visual festivals.

MN Mounting Solutions is a supplier of cost-effective mounting hardware for professional audio & projection equipment. With its many years of expertise  in producing custom mounting accessories for touring, fixed installations and professional cinema, today MN Mounting Solutions provides readily available, easy to install, cost effective & high quality solutions for numerous areas:

- Aim-able brackets for wall speaker mounting;
- Multi Axis Ceiling speaker mounting and aiming systems;
- Cinema projector pedestals;
- 19” rack stands and accessories and more.

We at MN Mounting Solutions are continuously working to provide superior flexibility and extend the usability range of our products. It is our goal to provide installation professionals around the world with the best available modern tools to ensure quick, safe and reliable Pro A/V equipment mounting.

[EN] With more than a decade of experience, Rabbits was created in Brazil but quickly took its work abroad and now is an international company specialized in videography projects, delivering quality and up to date cinematic footage for brands and clients. As a technology-driven and creative studio, we have an in-house VFX, animation and 3D team. We are experts in creative images for a variety of commercial, corporate, events and media clients. Our vision is to provide seamless and unparalleled services in the videography field.
