THE WHY

After working with global brands like Red Bull and National Geographic, we saw a unique opportunity in mining — an industry rich in innovation, transformation, and untold stories.

That’s why we launched Mining Creative, a media house dedicated to elevating how mining communicates with the world. We studied traditional investor relation firms, marketing companies and media providers and quickly came to the conclusion that they’re stuck in the past; doing the bare minimum. We leverage our experience in a broad range of subject matter to create energetic and modern media that truly captivates the viewer.

WHAT WE DO

We're bringing the mining industry into the 21st century by utilising timelapse & drone technology to engage prospective investors and the general public in a fast paced, easy to digest manner.

WE PRODUCE

// Corporate brand videos

// Safety and training content

// Investor-facing presentations

// High-impact aerial/drone visuals

// Social media-ready deliverables

All designed with your audience in mind — whether that’s shareholders, regulators, community partners, or internal teams.

WHO WE WORK WITH

We’ve proudly worked with some of Australia’s leading junior mining and exploration companies, including Brightstar Resources (ASX: BTR), Horizon Minerals (ASX: HRZ), Medallion Metals (ASX: MM8) and Great Boulder Resources (ASX: GBR), to help communicate their projects with clarity and impact.

WHY OUR PARTNERS TRUST US

// We understand the compliance and safety standards of working on-site.

// Our team has experience creating in some of the most remote regions in Australia and worldwide.

// We speak your language — whether it’s talking drill programs, JORC compliance, or ESG reporting.

READY TO ELEVATE YOUR COMPANY’S STORY?

